{
  "id": 5162799714795520,
  "name": "Nested view transitions groups",
  "summary": "Allow view-transitions to generate a nested pseudo-element tree rather than a flat one.\r\n\r\nThis allows the view transition to appear more in line with its original elements and visual intent, as it enables clipping, nested 3D transforms, and proper application of effects like opacity, masking and filters.",
